<h3 class="h3TabContent">Pro+ Ranges</h3>
<h4>Dual Fuel Self-Cleaning Professional Convection Ranges</h4>
<img src="images/aga/pro-plus-stoverange-blk-300x300.jpg" alt="AGA Pro+ Ranges" class="imageFloat2" />
<p>Flexible for your changing needs, this modern range is loaded with rich features and energy saving benefits. It is the perfect choice for the environmentally conscious and avid chef.</p>
<p>The PRO+ delivers an impressive 4.9 cu. ft. of capacity. With twin fans to ensure even cooking throughout, there is plenty of room for those special holiday meals.</p>
<p>Powerful gas burners and a multifunction electric oven give you incredible flexibility and versatility. Burners operate on both natural gas or liquid propane (LP kit included), and range in strength from 5,000 to an outstanding 15,000 BTUs. The electric oven has multiple cooking settings and an ingenious Energy Saving Panel (ESP) that allows you to divide the oven cavity to save energy.</p>
